- module_ctrl1: Control Module 1 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl1_switch, ctrl1_cable_in_pos, ctrl1_cable_in_neg, ctrl1_cable_out_pos, ctrl1_cable_out_neg)
- module_ctrl2: Control Module 2 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl2_switch, ctrl2_cable_in_pos, ctrl2_cable_in_neg, ctrl2_cable_out_pos, ctrl2_cable_out_neg)
- module_ctrl3: Control Module 3 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl3_switch, ctrl3_cable_in_pos, ctrl3_cable_in_neg, ctrl3_cable_out_pos, ctrl3_cable_out_neg)
- module_ctrl4: Control Module 4 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl4_switch, ctrl4_cable_in_pos, ctrl4_cable_in_neg, ctrl4_cable_out_pos, ctrl4_cable_out_neg)
- module_ctrl5: Control Module 5 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl5_switch, ctrl5_cable_in_pos, ctrl5_cable_in_neg, ctrl5_cable_out_pos, ctrl5_cable_out_neg)
- module_ctrl6: Control Module 6 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl6_switch, ctrl6_cable_in_pos, ctrl6_cable_in_neg, ctrl6_cable_out_pos, ctrl6_cable_out_neg)
- module_ctrl7: Control Module 7 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl7_switch, ctrl7_cable_in_pos, ctrl7_cable_in_neg, ctrl7_cable_out_pos, ctrl7_cable_out_neg)
- module_ctrl8: Control Module 8 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl8_switch, ctrl8_cable_in_pos, ctrl8_cable_in_neg, ctrl8_cable_out_pos, ctrl8_cable_out_neg)
- module_load: Load Module (Components that are part of the module: main_bulb, internal_bulb, load_peephole, load_diode, load_cable_pos, load_cable_neg)

Individual Components:
- module_psu: Power Supply Module
- cube_psu: Power Supply Cube
- battery: Battery [inside enclosure: cube_psu]
- psu_green_led: PSU Status LED (green) [inside enclosure: cube_psu]
- psu_green_resistor: PSU Green LED Resistor [inside enclosure: cube_psu]
- psu_cable_pos: PSU Output Cable (+)
- psu_cable_neg: PSU Output Cable (−)
- battery_internal_resistor: Battery Internal Resistor [inside enclosure: cube_psu]
- module_ctrl1: Control Module 1
- cube_ctrl1: Control Cube 1
- ctrl1_switch: Control Switch 1 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl1]
- ctrl1_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 1
- ctrl1_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 1
- ctrl1_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 1
- ctrl1_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 1
- module_ctrl2: Control Module 2
- cube_ctrl2: Control Cube 2
- ctrl2_switch: Control Switch 2 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl2]
- ctrl2_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 2
- ctrl2_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 2
- ctrl2_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 2
- ctrl2_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 2
- module_ctrl3: Control Module 3
- cube_ctrl3: Control Cube 3
- ctrl3_switch: Control Switch 3 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl3]
- ctrl3_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 3
- ctrl3_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 3
- ctrl3_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 3
- ctrl3_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 3
- module_ctrl4: Control Module 4
- cube_ctrl4: Control Cube 4
- ctrl4_switch: Control Switch 4 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl4]
- ctrl4_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 4
- ctrl4_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 4
- ctrl4_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 4
- ctrl4_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 4
- module_ctrl5: Control Module 5
- cube_ctrl5: Control Cube 5
- ctrl5_switch: Control Switch 5 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl5]
- ctrl5_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 5
- ctrl5_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 5
- ctrl5_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 5
- ctrl5_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 5
- module_ctrl6: Control Module 6
- cube_ctrl6: Control Cube 6
- ctrl6_switch: Control Switch 6 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl6]
- ctrl6_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 6
- ctrl6_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 6
- ctrl6_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 6
- ctrl6_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 6
- module_ctrl7: Control Module 7
- cube_ctrl7: Control Cube 7
- ctrl7_switch: Control Switch 7 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl7]
- ctrl7_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 7
- ctrl7_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 7
- ctrl7_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 7
- ctrl7_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 7
- module_ctrl8: Control Module 8
- cube_ctrl8: Control Cube 8
- ctrl8_switch: Control Switch 8 [inside enclosure: cube_ctrl8]
- ctrl8_cable_in_pos: Control Input Cable (+) 8
- ctrl8_cable_in_neg: Control Input Cable (−) 8
- ctrl8_cable_out_pos: Control Output Cable (+) 8
- ctrl8_cable_out_neg: Control Output Cable (−) 8
- module_load: Load Module
- cube_load: Load Cube
- load_peephole: Load Cube Peephole [inside enclosure: cube_load] [NOTE: This is an access hole on the load cube, not a sensor or light source. To look inside: first call open_peephole on load_peephole, then call observe_component on internal_bulb.]
- main_bulb: Main Load (lamp) [inside enclosure: cube_load]
- internal_bulb: Internal Indicator Lamp [inside enclosure: cube_load] [NOTE: This lamp is connected in parallel with the main load and reflects voltage conditions across that branch.]
- load_diode: Load Protection Diode [inside enclosure: cube_load]
- load_cable_pos: Load Input Cable (+)
- load_cable_neg: Load Input Cable (−)
- ctrl1_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 1
- ctrl1_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 1
- ctrl2_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 2
- ctrl2_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 2
- ctrl3_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 3
- ctrl3_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 3
- ctrl4_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 4
- ctrl4_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 4
- ctrl5_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 5
- ctrl5_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 5
- ctrl6_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 6
- ctrl6_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 6
- ctrl7_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 7
- ctrl7_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 7
- ctrl8_green_led: Power Flow Indicator (green) 8
- ctrl8_green_resistor: Power Flow Indicator Resistor 8

Instruction: Visually inspect each plug/socket pair between adjacent modules (PSU→CM1→…→CM8→Load). For every junction, check that the two fast‑connection terminals are mated in the same left/right (or top/bottom) orientation on both modules, and that no connector pair is rotated 180° or cross‑plugged into the wrong side, which would swap the positive and negative conductors to downstream modules.
